    <h3 class="title"><a href="/scatter-bluetooth-keyboards-everywhere#comment-5464" class="active">the new rage is ultra-mobile laptops</a></h3>    <div class="submitted">Submitted by Fry (not verified) on Tue, 2008-06-10 12:08.</div>
    <div class="content"><p>So...  What would be your choice for the above?  I'm looking at the ASUS Eee PC.  Anything else compare?  I'm at the crossroads of buying either a smartphone or pda or one of these...  For the price, looks like it might be my best best over a phone for functionality, at least until the next gen of smartphones emerges...</p>
</div>
